  "analysis": "The hvac_simulator.py file exists and provides an HVACSimulator class. The simulator implements a first-order thermal system with unknown K and tau parameters that I need to identify. It has methods for getting ambient temp, dt, safety limits, and setpoint. I need to see more methods like step() or update() to understand how to interact with it.",
