  "analysis": "All 5 required JSON files are present and properly formatted. The current results show: rise_time=85s, overshoot=3.59%, steady_state_error=0.11C (all excellent), but settling_time=223s (above 120s target). The variation in settling time between runs (152s vs 223s) suggests the system is sensitive to the identified tau parameter. Let me try lambda_factor=0.26 as a compromise, which might give better settling time than 0.25.",
